{"tid":997663,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"roomate放屁好撚臭","createTime":"2019-01-27T10:48:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-27T15:25:16.000Z","uid":64601,"like":179,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"5c54d3650954acf1dd7c2ce7a39700ee193cec3b","tid":997663,"uid":64601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T10:48:31.000Z","msg":"是咁的，最近嚟咗個新roomate，肥肥地毒撚嚟，咁冇咩啦，第一日打下招呼幾nice咁，但有啲嘢頂唔撚順，就係佢瞓教好！撚！鍾！意！放！屁！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁都冇咩，放屁人之常情，但原來佢一熟睡就係撚咁放，仲要係濕屁嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，條友平時食開煎炸嘢，又少菜，痾屎全層都成日聽到佢痾爛屎，我行過都唔好意思。<br />\n<br />\n你知㗎啦，冬天梗係襟實張被，條友又有鼻寒，啫係乜鳩都聞唔到用口唞氣。有時啲屎屁漏咗出嚟，就好似有個人肉屎塔喺隔離，臭到瞓唔到，聽日仲要八半堂，就嚟痴線。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁佢有張良計，我有達文西，就係喺床邊開行風扇，係撚咁吹，咁就做成熱帶氣旋，陣味就冇咁濃，但凍到pk。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有次佢醒咗，佢問我做咩開風扇嘅？我著哂羽絨，係咁震話：天口熱，想吹下海風嘛。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我都唔知自己噏緊乜鳩。佢話哦，就瞓撚咗。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n又有次佢轉身成張被掀起咗，臭到風扇都冇用，我狗衝幫佢襟返好，整醒咗佢，佢問我做咩，我話：驚你凍親嘛。仲讚返我暖男。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n屌那星而家連火都唔敢喺房開，驚會爆炸，有冇巴絲可以教我點做先可以脫離呢個放屁怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3300e6edf05e24d0fb00c34a4c13010c6b1f82ef","tid":997663,"uid":2446,"like":0,"dislike":11,"score":-11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T10:48:45.000Z","msg":"10/100"},{"pid":"ac9974651d5f12e7ccd7dceaea4cb0d548c168a8","tid":997663,"uid":62348,"like":93,"dislike":0,"score":93,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T10:51:24.000Z","msg":"馬鳩而家連潮文界都撈埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f9f5f524e59c1968b0a2b476cf544c04a7cd11f","tid":997663,"uid":64601,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"ac9974651d5f12e7ccd7dceaea4cb0d548c168a8","tid":997663,"uid":62348,"like":93,"dislike":0,"score":93,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T10:51:24.000Z","msg":"馬鳩而家連潮文界都撈埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T10:51:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />真人真事"},{"pid":"dcc162833bc1bbd86d69a663360eb1f1dc75bc01","tid":997663,"uid":212317,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T10:52:11.000Z","msg":"殺左佢  <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93a0c0df26285817b3dbe607fb37ea800bf5ae00","tid":997663,"uid":199371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T10:52:43.000Z","msg":"10/10<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n冇得調房咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e657dc5d488d70119f98c2d63ebc2ebc20e40851","tid":997663,"uid":7347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T10:52:52.000Z","msg":"10/10"},{"pid":"651e35bae38bbaab1a32e639325f92d7e1bb2a72","tid":997663,"uid":64601,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"dcc162833bc1bbd86d69a663360eb1f1dc75bc01","tid":997663,"uid":212317,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T10:52:11.000Z","msg":"殺左佢  <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T10:53:07.000Z","msg":"有諗過開打火機一鑊熟<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=